from time to time to ensure that you are happy with any changes.
By using the Service, you are expressing your
agreement to this policy and the processing of your data, including your
personal information as described in the policy. Should you have a disagreement
with our policy, please do not use the Service. You can contact us for concerns
and questions regarding this policy via email at:
